Title: Fixed broken BI availability with limit set to 0 (regression in 1.4.0p26)
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
State: unknown
Version: 1.5.0b1
Date: 1522820887

In case you are affected, you can set the availability limit to another value than
0 to workaround this issue.
